OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773284607
OL,3,CHousing market 'struggling for
OL,4,Cmomentum amid global uncertainty'
OL,6,FThe housing market is struggling for
OL,7,Fmomentum as global and economic
OL,8,Funcertainties weigh on home buyer
OL,9,Fsentiment, according to surveyors.
OL,11,FThe Royal Institution of Chartered
OL,12,FSurveyors (Rics) said that while some
OL,13,Fsurveyors reported a more encouraging
OL,14,Fstart to the year, confidence weakened
OL,15,Fas concerns over inflation, interest
OL,16,Frates and global instability
OL,17,Fintensified.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773284607
OL,3,CHousing market 'struggling for
OL,4,Cmomentum amid global uncertainty'
OL,6,FNew buyer inquiries weakened further
OL,7,Fin February, with a net balance of 26%
OL,8,Fof property professionals reporting
OL,9,Ffalls in inquiries rather than rises,
OL,10,Fdeteriorating from a balance of 15%
OL,11,Fwho saw this in January.
OL,13,FAgreed sales also remained subdued,
OL,14,Fwith a net balance of 12% of property
OL,15,Fprofessionals reporting falls.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773284607
OL,3,CHousing market 'struggling for
OL,4,Cmomentum amid global uncertainty'
OL,6,FThe report said that overall,
OL,7,Fprofessionals also expect sales to
OL,8,Ffall in the near term, but in the
OL,9,Flonger term the outlook remains more
OL,10,Fresilient, with a net balance of 17%
OL,11,Fprofessionals expecting sales activity
OL,12,Fto pick up over the next 12 months.
OL,14,FHouse prices were broadly flat overall
OL,15,Fin February, with a net balance of 12%
OL,16,Fof professionals reporting falls, but
OL,17,Fthere were big regional variations,
OL,18,FRics said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773284607
OL,3,CHousing market 'struggling for
OL,4,Cmomentum amid global uncertainty'
OL,6,FDownward price pressure is
OL,7,Fparticularly strong in London, the
OL,8,FSouth East and East Anglia, while
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland, Scotland and the
OL,10,FNorth West of England are still
OL,11,Freporting firmer price trends,
OL,12,Faccording to the report.
OL,14,FLooking ahead, surveyors have become
OL,15,Fmore cautious about house prices in
OL,16,Fthe near term, but looking further
OL,17,Fahead to the next 12 months a net
OL,18,Fbalance of 33% of professionals are
OL,19,Fexpecting prices to edge higher.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773284607
OL,3,CHousing market 'struggling for
OL,4,Cmomentum amid global uncertainty'
OL,6,FBut in London, expectations for house
OL,7,Fprices in the next 12 months have
OL,8,F"cooled sharply", the report found.
OL,10,FOn the supply side, new instructions
OL,11,Fremained broadly stable in February,
OL,12,Findicating little immediate shift in
OL,13,Fthe pipeline of new stock.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
