FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773284607
OL,3,CHousing market 'struggling for
OL,4,Cmomentum amid global uncertainty'
OL,6,FIn the lettings market, tenant demand
OL,7,Fwas broadly stable over the three
OL,8,Fmonths to February, but landlord
OL,9,Finstructions were "firmly negative",
OL,10,Fpointing to a shortage of rental
OL,11,Fhomes. Professionals are expecting
OL,12,Frents to rise overall in the next
OL,13,Fthree months, the report found.
OL,15,FMortgage lenders have been withdrawing
OL,16,Fdeals and increasing their rates as
OL,17,Fswap rates have increased, with
OL,18,Fconcerns about rising prices mounting
OL,19,Famid the conflict in the Middle East.
OL,26,@qD@SOUqD@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
