OL,3,CHousing market 'struggling for
OL,4,Cmomentum amid global uncertainty'
OL,6,FFinancial information website
OL,7,FMoneyfactscompare.co.uk said on
OL,8,FWednesday that recent days have been
OL,9,Fsome of the most turbulent in the UK
OL,10,Fmortgage market since the aftermath of
OL,11,Fthe September 2022 mini-budget.
OL,13,FSome average mortgage rates on the
OL,14,Fmarket have also flown past the 5%
OL,15,Fmark as lenders have scrambled to make
OL,16,Fchanges.
OL,18,FRics head of market research and
OL,19,Fanalytics, Tarrant Parsons, said:
OL,20,F"February's survey highlights renewed
OL,21,Fvolatility in the market.
OL,26,@|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773284607
OL,3,CHousing market 'struggling for
OL,4,Cmomentum amid global uncertainty'
OL,6,F"While activity indicators at the
OL,7,Fstart of the year suggested a
OL,8,Ftentative improvement, the
OL,9,Fdeterioration in the geopolitical
OL,10,Fbackdrop has clearly weighed on
OL,11,Fconfidence.
OL,13,F"The recent rise in oil and energy
OL,14,Fprices has also increased the
OL,15,Flikelihood that mortgage rates will
OL,16,Fremain higher for longer.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1773284607
OL,3,CHousing market 'struggling for
OL,4,Cmomentum amid global uncertainty'
OL,6,F"As a result, near-term expectations
OL,7,Fhave softened. Although the 12-month
OL,8,Foutlook remains positive overall,
OL,9,Fmaintaining that trajectory will
OL,10,Fdepend on the recent spike in
OL,11,Finflationary pressures easing in the
OL,12,Fmonths ahead."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@NO]
